hopobject.body: How many days will it take for the cheque to clear? essentia health pharmacy virginia mn Remembered more for the fuss it caused than its lasting power, Howard Brenton’s revisiting of the Roman invasion of Celtic Britain in its brutal colonial aspects may have done little more than suggest that all imperial roads led to Northern Ireland but it became a cause célèbre that helped define the National. Its denunciation by the campaigner Mary Whitehouse – outraged at its simulated male rape – resulted in many column inches, the hysterical episode climaxing in the sudden withdrawal of her doomed private prosecution. The theatre emerged vindicated and validated.
